{"version": 2, "width": 100, "height": 30, "timestamp": 1778789087, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}, "title": "HELIX evolve: thread a new requirement through the artifact graph"}
[0.0, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m# The classic example from the product vision: 'We want OAuth login.' One sentence. The evolve skill walks the depends_on graph in both directions and orders updates by authority.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.0, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m> /helix-evolve Add OAuth login alongside the existing API-key auth. Walk the depends_on graph in both directions and order updates by authority.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.0, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Skill(skill='helix', args='evolve: Add OAuth login alongside the existing API-key auth')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.5, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 Launching skill: helix\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.8, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Bash(command=\"find docs/helix -type f -not -path '*/.*'\", description='Enumerate governing artifacts')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.3, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 docs/helix/02-design/security-architecture.md\r\ndocs/helix/01-frame/features/FEAT-AUTH.md\r\ndocs/helix/01-frame/prd.md\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.6, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='docs/helix/01-frame/prd.md')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.1, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 38 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.4, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='docs/helix/01-frame/features/FEAT-AUTH.md')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.9, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 24 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.2, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2699 Read(file_path='docs/helix/02-design/security-architecture.md')\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.7, "o", "\u001b[2m  \u2192 23 lines\u001b[0m\r\n"]
